1
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,080
Well,

2
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:54,520
come on. Let's toast to our fleeting youth

3
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,880
and the end of the college entrance exam.

4
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,560
Since the results will be out tomorrow,

5
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,920
let's all have a drink together.

6
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,180
Okay, come on. Cheers!

7
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:00,880
Cheers!

8
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:01,740
Cheers!

9
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:04,200
Cheers!

10
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,720
Cheers!

11
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:13,080
The math questions in this year's exam were too difficult.

12
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,600
I don't know how others did.

13
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,320
Anyway,

14
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:17,079
I'm ready to retake the exam.

15
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,680
Didn't you throw away all your books?

16
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,340
How are you going to retake it?

17
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,120
Right.

18
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,320
I was too hasty.

19
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,200
Don't be discouraged.

20
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,720
Maybe when the results come out tomorrow,

21
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,250
you'll surprise everyone.

22
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:29,960
Come on.

23
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,680
Do you think everyone is Qingyun?

24
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,610
With our scores,

25
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:34,000
we should know where we stand.

26
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:34,800
That's right.

27
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,440
Will it kill you not to be sarcastic?

28
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:38,700
Ruirui, why aren't you saying anything?

29
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,040
You guys are having such a lively chat,

30
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,370
I couldn't get a word in.

31
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,840
Ruirui, didn't you estimate your score

32
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:45,800
to be 610?

33
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,800
But I'm not sure if my estimate is accurate.

34
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,200
You guys can actually remember the answers?

35
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,520
I can't even remember the ones I guessed.

36
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,220
Class Monitor,

37
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,000
aren't you going to study abroad?

38
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,880
Can we ask you to buy things for us

39
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:02,160
in the future?

40
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,640
Okay.

41
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,160
You're going to study abroad.

42
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,280
Why didn't you tell me?

43
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,880
Where are you going to study?

44
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,640
I'm going to London.

45
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,680
London.

46
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,760
That's a big city.

47
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,640
Then won't you be able to see Qingyun?

48
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:14,920
Yeah.

49
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,920
L-London is so big.

50
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,840
I might not necessarily see him.

51
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,240
What's wrong?

52
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,880
Let's sing together.

53
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,040
Let's sing.

54
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:46,040
I miss him so much.

55
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,280
I know.

56
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,920
I really miss him.

57
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,320
I know.

58
00:04:57,800 --> 00:05:00,000
I really want to tell him

59
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:03,840
that I really like him.

60
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,720
He will know.

61
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,400
But,

62
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:15,600
I will never see him again.

63
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,880
Yuanbao, you still have me.

64
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:20,680
I

65
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,680
will always stay by your side

66
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,610
and protect you.

67
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,920
So,

68
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,520
you are not alone.

69
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,290
Don't be afraid.

70
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:45,800
Mom, Dad,

71
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,040
Grandma,

72
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,930
I got into a university in Beijing.

73
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,080
Grandma,

74
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,360
I didn't let you down.

75
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:57,360
It's a really good university.

76
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,640
I'll be going to Beijing in a few days.

77
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,680
I might not be able to visit you for a while.

78
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,480
Don't worry.

79
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,090
I will take good care of myself.

80
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,040
Grandma,

81
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:16,200
Please bless Mutou's family

82
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,320
and keep them all safe.

83
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:31,960
You're here.

84
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,159
Ruirui.

85
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,140
This is for you.

86
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,760
What do you mean?

87
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,320
Actually,

88
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,000
I've thought it through.

89
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:52,100
These things of yours,

90
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,520
I wanted to give them back to you

91
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:56,120
when we went to college together.

92
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,040
But

93
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,760
now I feel like we might

94
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,650
not be right for each other.

95
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:08,480
We are just good friends.

96
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:15,480
What exactly are you trying to say?

97
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,280
I just want to say,

98
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,120
we are just good friends.

99
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,130
Focus on your college studies,

100
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,600
and don't wait for me.

101
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,620
Here, take this as a souvenir.

102
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,159
You pervert!

103
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,140
Taking photos of me secretly.

104
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:04,680
I'm sorry.

105
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:09,740
You were the one who said you wanted to pursue me.

106
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,960
Then you said we were not suitable.

107
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,200
Why did you do this

108
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,760
to me?

109
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:22,260
I was afraid of affecting your college entrance examination before.

110
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:26,570
But now you have received your admission letter.

111
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,770
I have no more concerns.

112
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,000
Anyway,

113
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:37,720
you understand what I mean anyway.

114
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,450
I'm leaving now.

115
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,800
Stop.

116
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,200
What?

117
00:08:56,960 --> 00:09:00,120
Afraid of holding me back because you didn't get into university,

118
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,580
or do you think you're not good enough for me?

119
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,520
Ruirui, you...

120
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,920
Those photos you secretly took of me,

121
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,000
If you really want to give them to me,

122
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,680
bring them to me in Shanghai.

123
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,920
I'll wait for you in Shanghai next year.

124
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:30,920
If you don't get in next year,

125
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,360
I'll...

126
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,160
I'll kill you.

127
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,160
What are you waiting for?

128
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,520
Hurry back and study.

129
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,500
Waiting for me to kick you out?

130
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,840
Okay, okay.

131
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,580
I... I'm going home right now.

132
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,960
Ruirui, then...

133
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,200
then wait for me.

134
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,800
You must wait for me.

135
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:02,080
Stop dawdling.

136
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:04,640
Wait for me.

137
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,160
Wait for me.

138
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,440
How is she so smart?

139
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:15,240
I can't hide anything from her.

140
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:18,040
Ruirui, you must wait for me in Shanghai next year.

141
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,440
Grandma.

142
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,240
Mutou.

143
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,440
I'm leaving.

144
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:08,160
Yuanbao.

145
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,320
Over here.

146
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:14,090
Let's go to school. We're almost late.

147
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:14,720
Let's go.

148
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,960
Yuanbao, let's hurry.

149
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,290
We're going to miss our flight.

150
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,720
Let's go, Mutou.

151
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,800
We're going to school.

152
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,200
Thank you

153
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,540
for giving me so many lucky stars.

154
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:13,130
They brought me to where I am today.

155
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:15,800
Auntie,

156
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:19,040
after you leave,

157
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:21,680
please help me pass these things

158
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,960
to Mutou.

159
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:28,120
I hope Mutou recovers and leaves the hospital soon.

160
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:30,250
I hope Mutou doesn't get sick anymore.

161
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:33,340
I hope Mutou's grades improve by ten places.

162
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,920
If not ten, five is fine too.

163
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:39,680
I hope Mutou finishes homework seriously from now on.

164
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,200
I hope I can save enough allowance.

165
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:45,400
give him an unforgettable New Year's gift.

166
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:49,280
I hope Mutou will like the food I cooked.

167
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,000
I hope Mutou and I

168
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:54,170
can both get into universities in Beijing smoothly.

169
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:56,320
I like Mutou.

170
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,880
I hope

171
00:12:58,560 --> 00:13:00,040
he likes me too.

172
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:45,440
Yuanbao, where on earth are you?

173
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:47,760
Qingyun,

174
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,280
I've been looking for you for so long.

175
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,610
So you were hiding here.

176
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:56,200
Let's go when you're ready.

177
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:58,520
We can't be late for the class reunion.

178
00:13:58,520 --> 00:13:59,280
Tell me,

179
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,400
will she see it?

180
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,440
What?

181
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,520
My work.

182
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:07,760
Will she see it?

183
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:12,690
All the heroines in your current works

184
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:14,760
are named after her.

185
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:17,560
And now you've won

186
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:20,020
the Best International New Director Award.

187
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,860
So she will definitely see it.

188
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:26,010
But why hasn't she shown up yet?

189
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:37,600
Qingyun,

190
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:42,700
you've been looking for Yuanbao for so many years with no news.

191
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:45,500
Are you really going to keep looking?

192
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:53,280
Maybe she'll suddenly appear.

193
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,090
So don't lose heart.

194
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,520
Will she?

195
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:03,200
Even if she doesn't,

196
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:06,540
as long as you believe,

197
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:09,620
you will definitely find her.

198
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,880
Over the years, among the things you wanted to do,

199
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:14,810
which one hasn't been successful?

200
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:16,880
So this time,

201
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:18,610
it will work out too.

202
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:21,440
Yaqi,

203
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:24,580
thanks for your hard work.

204
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,120
Thank you.

205
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:29,160
I never feel it's hard work.

206
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,000
Besides,

207
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:34,180
I don't need you to say thank you to me.

208
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:37,760
If you have to say something,

209
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:40,360
I hope

210
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,380
it's those other three words.

211
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:00,920
He's coming.

212
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:04,480
Director Mu.

213
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,480
Director Mu.

214
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:06,400
Director Mu.

215
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:07,560
Director Mu.

216
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:13,120
Don't push. Okay.

217
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:15,120
Everyone, step back a little.

218
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,920
Thank you for your cooperation.

219
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:21,920
Director Mu.

220
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:28,880
Director Mu.

221
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:30,720
Rumor has it that you're getting engaged to Miss Xing soon.

222
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:31,600
Is it true?

223
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:33,600
Director Mu, is what they say online true?

224
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:34,680
When will the wedding be set?

225
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:36,920
Director Mu, please say a few words to our fans.

226
00:16:36,920 --> 00:16:37,560
Director Mu, could you please

227
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:39,360
say a few words to us? Director Mu.

228
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,360
Director Mu.

229
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:42,090
Director Mu, please look here.

230
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,400
Director Mu.

231
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:46,680
What about our exclusive interview next, Director Mu?

232
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:47,360
Director Mu, don't go.

233
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,280
Say a few words to us.

234
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:49,540
Don't go. Director Mu.

235
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:51,520
Director Mu, keep it up.

236
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,960
Director Mu, please accept our exclusive interview.

237
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,520
All right. Step back.

238
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:57,000
Don't push.

239
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:59,290
What's wrong, Qingyun?

240
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,040
Nothing.

241
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:04,520
Director Mu, please answer our questions.

242
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:25,720
Everyone,

243
00:17:25,839 --> 00:17:28,520
as the initiator of this gathering,

244
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,210
I'll propose a toast first.

245
00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:33,000
Today marks the 10th anniversary of our admission.

246
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:33,880
We are also very honored

247
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:36,160
to have invited a few of our teachers and classmates here.

248
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,640
Here, I propose

249
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:38,920
that we offer our first toast

250
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:40,080
to our

251
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,580
most respected teachers,

252
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:43,920
wishing them good health and peace.

253
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:44,440
How about that?

254
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:45,160
Yes!

255
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,240
Let's do it together.

256
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:47,800
Come on.

257
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:49,960
Come on, together.

258
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:50,800
Cheers.

259
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:56,880
Eat and drink well, everyone.

260
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:59,320
I heard you recently opened another branch.

261
00:17:59,320 --> 00:18:00,960
You have two hotels now, right?

262
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:03,680
You are a true tycoon now.

263
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:05,160
What tycoon?

264
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,960
I'm just a small restaurant owner.

265
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,000
If we're talking about being impressive,

266
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:10,060
it has to be Meng Jingu and Mu Qingyun.

267
00:18:10,120 --> 00:18:11,480
One is a great scientist,

268
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:12,960
and the other is a famous director.

269
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:14,490
Director Mu arrived today.

270
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:16,320
The reporters and fans

271
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:18,240
completely blocked my hotel.

272
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:23,040
Today we have no great scientists

273
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:24,360
or great directors.

274
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:26,000
We are all classmates today.

275
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:26,680
Right.

276
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:29,210
We are all the same as ten years ago.

277
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,360
Nothing has changed.

278
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:31,840
Well said.

279
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:33,960
The friendship between classmates

280
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:35,360
is the purest.

281
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:38,500
No matter how many years pass, it will never change.

282
00:18:38,840 --> 00:18:41,080
It's just that it's been too long.

283
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,800
Some of the students' names,

284
00:18:43,040 --> 00:18:44,560
I can't even remember.

285
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:46,760
You see, Mr. Tian's memory

286
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:48,290
is getting worse and worse.

287
00:18:49,120 --> 00:18:50,080
Forgive him.

288
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:52,560
His mind is full of Ms. Xu right now.

289
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:53,520
Right?

290
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:55,520
But seriously, guys.

291
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:57,360
You've changed so much in ten years.

292
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:59,560
I wouldn't recognize you on the street.

293
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:01,000
Ruirui.

294
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:03,920
When is the baby due?

295
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:06,240
The due date is the 13th of next month.

296
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,240
That's great!

297
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,000
Ruirui.

298
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:11,100
I didn't expect you to end up marrying Shang Ningyu.

299
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:12,200
Don't mention it.

300
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:13,440
Our love story

301
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,680
has been quite bumpy.

302
00:19:15,120 --> 00:19:16,400
Tell us about it.

303
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,240
Tell us.

304
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:19,160
I've never heard you talk about it.

305
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:21,600
As for me, you know my grades were pretty bad back in school.

306
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,760
I failed the college entrance exam time and time again.

307
00:19:23,760 --> 00:19:25,560
So I went to Shanghai to make a living.

308
00:19:25,560 --> 00:19:27,400
I accompanied Ruirui while she studied,

309
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:29,530
and opened a small restaurant myself.

310
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:31,720
We've been through a lot of ups and downs

311
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:33,200
to get to where we are today.

312
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:35,330
So I am especially grateful to my wife.

313
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:37,440
Not only did she discover my cooking skills,

314
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:38,280
but every decision along the way,

315
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:40,280
big or small, was made by her.

316
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:41,920
If it weren't for Ruirui,

317
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,680
I, Shang Ningyu, wouldn't be here today.

318
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:46,880
So much time has passed in a flash.

319
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,760
Our school days

320
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,800
feel like just yesterday.

321
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:52,980
Let's make a toast.

322
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:53,520
Cheers.

323
00:19:53,520 --> 00:19:54,560
Come on.

324
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:56,400
Come on, everyone together.

325
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,480
Altogether.

326
00:19:57,680 --> 00:19:58,840
Bottoms up.

327
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:02,400
Come, drink up.

328
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:07,400
I'm so happy today.

329
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,800
But since Yuanbao isn't here,

330
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:11,800
it feels like something is missing.

331
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,400
But I heard from my wife

332
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:15,200
that she was supposed to come.

333
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:21,720
Qingyun,

334
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:23,040
I want to tell you something.

335
00:20:23,040 --> 00:20:24,120
Back in school,

336
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:27,740
Yuanbao intentionally made me get close to her.

337
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:28,600
The purpose

338
00:20:29,760 --> 00:20:31,560
was to make you go study in the UK.

339
00:20:36,760 --> 00:20:37,960
In college,

340
00:20:38,600 --> 00:20:39,800
we kept in touch a lot.

341
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:41,640
After graduation,

342
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:44,280
she moved to several cities,

343
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,160
and we lost touch.

344
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:50,440
You two were together in Beijing.

345
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:52,960
I thought you would end up together.

346
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,120
As for her,

347
00:20:54,560 --> 00:20:56,560
she always had someone in her heart,

348
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:58,520
and no one could replace him.

349
00:20:59,040 --> 00:20:59,800
Qingyun.

350
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:03,120
I heard that the class monitor

351
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:04,800
has been with you all these years.

352
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:06,400
So, you two...

353
00:21:06,880 --> 00:21:09,080
Our relationship is not what you think.

354
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:10,760
Abao Pictures.

355
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,560
Every production

356
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:14,640
has a girl named Yuanbao.

357
00:21:15,320 --> 00:21:16,520
Who is on his mind?

358
00:21:16,760 --> 00:21:17,800
Don't you know?

359
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:20,160
So devoted, bro.

360
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,850
But you've been out of touch for years.

361
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:25,760
What if she already has kids?

362
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:34,050
Just left like that?

363
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,360
You are too slow.

364
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,300
Hold it steady.

365
00:23:27,600 --> 00:23:28,440
Slow down.

366
00:23:30,080 --> 00:23:31,080
Cover that up.

367
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:35,480
Watch your hands.

368
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:36,610
That's about right.

369
00:23:39,120 --> 00:23:40,120
Move the cabinet.

370
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:47,480
Done.

371
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:59,480
Are you looking for someone?

372
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:03,250
Who told you to decorate this place like this?

373
00:24:03,360 --> 00:24:04,200
Who are you?

374
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,980
I'm the previous owner of this house.

375
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:11,200
These are our old furniture from over a decade ago.

376
00:24:15,040 --> 00:24:16,100
So it really is you.

377
00:24:37,600 --> 00:24:39,060
How do you have this photo?

378
00:24:39,600 --> 00:24:41,200
A Ms. Xiong

379
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:42,300
bought this house,

380
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:44,440
and asked us to follow this photo

381
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,840
to decorate it like this.

382
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:53,320
Yuanbao.

383
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:56,400
Yuanbao.

384
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,640
Do you know where she is now?

385
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:09,200
She just left. She shouldn't have gone far.

386
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,120
When did you get back?

387
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:13,400
A few days ago.

388
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:16,720
By the way.

389
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:18,200
Congratulations

390
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:20,210
on becoming a big director.

391
00:26:21,320 --> 00:26:22,450
I saw the video of you

392
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:26,200
and Yaqi at the awards ceremony.

393
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:29,800
She is

394
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:32,580
really beautiful.

395
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:44,640
You

396
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:47,120
got married.

397
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,500
Congratulations.

398
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:01,120
Thanks.

399
00:27:02,320 --> 00:27:03,400
You...

400
00:27:04,800 --> 00:27:05,720
you go first.

401
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:11,440
How have you been these past few years?

402
00:27:13,800 --> 00:27:14,600
Not bad.

403
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:16,660
What about you?

404
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:19,340
I'm doing pretty well too.

405
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:22,660
The flowers in front of Grandma's grave,

406
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:24,860
you put them there, right?

407
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:28,690
I haven't been back for a long time.

408
00:27:29,080 --> 00:27:30,140
I should visit her.

409
00:27:31,320 --> 00:27:34,000
By the way, how are your mom and dad doing?

410
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,610
They are doing well.

411
00:27:37,560 --> 00:27:38,880
Both have retired

412
00:27:39,440 --> 00:27:40,570
and gone traveling.

413
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:48,440
Do you love him?

414
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:53,480
I heard you organized a class reunion yesterday.

415
00:27:54,160 --> 00:27:56,120
Everyone must have changed a lot.

416
00:27:57,320 --> 00:27:58,360
Do you love him?

417
00:28:02,280 --> 00:28:05,600
I heard Qiao Yan had a baby.

418
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:07,880
She's a mother now.

419
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:10,320
Time really flies.

420
00:28:11,160 --> 00:28:12,000
So,

421
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:14,000
do you love him?

422
00:28:19,600 --> 00:28:21,640
I have things to do, so I'll leave first.

423
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:22,320
Goodbye.

424
00:28:40,800 --> 00:28:41,520
Come on.

425
00:28:44,080 --> 00:28:45,120
You are so bad.

426
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:46,700
You are bullying me again.

427
00:28:48,760 --> 00:28:49,620
Don't touch me.

428
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:01,800
Come down.

429
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:03,240
Blockhead.

430
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:04,040
Stop right there.

431
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:05,600
Come catch me.

432
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:20,130
Director Mu.

433
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,360
So in your

434
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:22,880
award-winning work this time,

435
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:24,540
there is a girl named Yuanbao.

436
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:25,880
In your previous work,

437
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:27,800
there was also a girl named Yuanbao.

438
00:29:27,800 --> 00:29:29,440
So many netizens are curious.

439
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:30,200
Is this Yuanbao

440
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:31,920
the one you love?

441
00:29:32,080 --> 00:29:32,920
Would it be convenient

442
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:34,120
to share with us

443
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:35,080
your story?

444
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:38,130
I have been looking for someone for nearly ten years.

445
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:40,400
I want her to be the leading actress in my movie.

446
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:43,200
I want to take her to Beijing to see the Bird's Nest.

447
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:45,560
I want to take her to Tiananmen Square to watch the flag-raising ceremony.

448
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:47,760
I want to spend the rest of my life with her.

449
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:49,400
Her name is Yuanbao.

450
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,520
That's so romantic!

451
00:29:56,800 --> 00:29:58,400
I believe countless female fans

452
00:29:58,400 --> 00:29:59,480
hearing such a story

453
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:00,920
would be moved to tears.

454
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:02,200
So at this moment,

455
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:03,800
what do you want to say to her

456
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:05,040
in front of the TV?

457
00:30:05,560 --> 00:30:09,000
The flower language of baby's breath is silent protection.

458
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:12,440
I used to protect her silently.

459
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:16,000
Now I want to continue to protect her.

460
00:30:24,040 --> 00:30:24,840
Yuanbao.

461
00:30:28,760 --> 00:30:29,880
Yaqi.

462
00:30:31,760 --> 00:30:32,480
Yuanbao,

463
00:30:32,760 --> 00:30:34,720
why didn't you come to the class reunion?

464
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:36,320
Everyone misses you so much.

465
00:30:39,280 --> 00:30:40,840
Married Mu Qingjun.

466
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:42,440
What are you talking about?

467
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,520
Of course not.

468
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,720
We are partners.

469
00:30:45,800 --> 00:30:47,000
Business partners.

470
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:50,400
You know what?

471
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:53,180
Actually, Qingjun has been looking for you.

472
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:56,180
Looking for me?

473
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:58,960
All these years,

474
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:01,540
he has never given up looking for you.

475
00:33:22,080 --> 00:33:24,040
A long time ago, there was a little girl.

476
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:26,960
Her tears could turn into sparkling diamonds,

477
00:33:27,120 --> 00:33:29,240
so people called her the Diamond Princess.

478
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:29,920
Your tears

479
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:32,250
have all turned into sparkling diamonds.

480
00:33:32,320 --> 00:33:34,600
This means you are also the Diamond Princess.

481
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:36,280
You must keep this diamond safe.

482
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:37,840
When you turn 18,

483
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:38,960
we will come back here.

484
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:39,880
Then we will know

485
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:41,610
what gift the elf will give you.

486
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:43,760
Miss,

487
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:44,720
we have many customers coming here

488
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:46,520
to customize diamond rings.

489
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:48,520
But you are the first one

490
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:50,160
to customize with broken glass.

491
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:52,690
Presumably, this small piece of broken glass

492
00:33:52,720 --> 00:33:54,720
It must have a very special meaning.

493
00:33:58,400 --> 00:33:59,120
Yes.

494
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:00,320
It was given to me

495
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:02,280
by someone very important to me.

496
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:07,400
You must come too.

497
00:34:08,159 --> 00:34:08,920
Definitely.

498
00:34:12,159 --> 00:34:15,760
If you were to act in 'A Chinese Odyssey' again,

499
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,449
you play Zhi Zun Bao,

500
00:34:19,719 --> 00:34:20,920
and I play Zixia,

501
00:34:23,159 --> 00:34:24,440
would you still do it?

502
00:34:28,480 --> 00:34:29,639
Then that's it.

503
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:31,940
The person I've been yearning

504
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:34,760
and longing for is back.

505
00:34:35,199 --> 00:34:36,199
Then that's it.

506
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,520
The person I've been yearning

507
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:41,280
and longing for is back.

508
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:40,440
Quick, make a wish!
